File Format: ICO (Windows Icon)
Dimensions: Multi-resolution icon containing 16x16, 32x32, and 48x48 pixel versions
Color Depth: 32-bit (True Color with Alpha)
Primary Color: #2563eb (Brand Blue)
Background: Transparent
Design: Minimalist "P" lettermark
File Size: Optimized for web delivery
Features:
- Alpha channel transparency
- Pixel-perfect hinting
- Dark/light theme adaptability
- High contrast ratio
- WCAG 2.1 AA compliant

The icon should be created using professional icon editing software with the following characteristics:

1. Design:
- Clean, minimalist "P" lettermark
- Primary brand color #2563eb
- Transparent background
- Crisp edges with anti-aliasing
- Pixel-perfect alignment

2. Multiple Resolutions:
- 16x16: Simplified version for browser tabs
- 32x32: Standard resolution for bookmarks
- 48x48: Enhanced detail for PWA and larger displays

3. Optimization:
- Lossless compression
- Pixel hinting enabled
- Optimized file size
- No color palette reduction

4. Technical Requirements:
- ICO format with embedded PNG data
- 32-bit color depth (24-bit color + 8-bit alpha)
- Proper alpha channel implementation
- Color profile: sRGB

The icon should be delivered with:
Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400
Content-Type: image/x-icon